n><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9b8a32bb-8a14-4c25-955d-e20c81980625\">을 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c5e3c76b-0d6d-4717-851b-e772ef1db1f4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a1628d7c-b0ae-46bf-826c-2bf0292fd8b6\">받으신 적 있으신가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-016f05b5-5bf0-433d-bc79-2bc207739128\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fa40c751-315a-4d77-9d7a-2b42ad111700\">이럴 때 한의학에서는 ‘배수혈(背腧穴)’이라는 중요한 개념을 살펴봅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-723fb6f3-bc78-4558-a512-1b523754088f\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c4edefbb-cbbf-4b49-b2ef-7c2fa1892ee1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c4edefbb-cbbf-4b49-b2ef-7c2fa1892ee1\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f5416092d36ca0de.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f5416092d36ca0de.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f5416092d36ca0de.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-c4edefbb-cbbf-4b49-b2ef-7c2fa1892ee1\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-1a1999da-d3c5-45df-9e5d-d3265714b8a6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7733008b-a637-4545-96f8-87f9e44e89cb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-93df9702-72b6-4441-bac3-e49dbcdd4bd6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-680b4240-66f0-42e2-b1b8-152427b99737\"><b>배수혈이란 무엇인가요?</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2925efea-f6ea-4018-9e33-739199308167\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2f56b6f8-6c55-44cf-88f3-d7bb87e11507\">‘배수혈’은 한의학에서 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-14630b45-5152-4e4c-a8ad-d3aefb77392e\"><b>등쪽 척추 양옆에 위치한 주요 경혈들</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6338f95a-cd7a-4694-917d-4b0fca2039b9\">을 말합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0df328c1-130b-42a8-a3e2-33ddc10bd1c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c89bc791-620b-42a2-89df-4a2b46dec942\">이 배수혈들은 단순한 지압점이 아니라, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-33ab7c3f-fc46-4fcf-96c8-0b1849541d0e\"><b>우리 몸의 장기와 직접 연결된 통로</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d99b2fb7-5f85-4edc-9f6c-1a9536d4307a\">입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-19e27e4e-b353-4d5d-8c88-3a9ee5a2c9e6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1a1ec52f-a431-4c12-8de5-c09e2558c581\">예를 들어,</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-108adbd7-cd30-45b1-9e3c-0b5bb79516b4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-589f0fb6-ef2c-43ef-9394-7de31372df24\">심장과 연결된 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-93954535-a00f-4a56-8269-43baa7664a81\"><b>심유혈(心兪穴)</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-812b9046-5a04-4946-acbe-6d41e98e9860\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6fde1bb3-351c-4862-8591-82e02db00a80\">폐와 연결된 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7e530208-087b-4a0d-ab2f-482057b8f8d8\"><b>폐유혈(肺兪穴)</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85d48e95-2259-44f1-ac75-646141fe9ec9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1b785847-3ce9-4890-822f-e8777e7abc14\">간과 연결된 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e4b00335-7ebd-4b9c-a0c2-a361f0de3df4\"><b>간유혈(肝兪穴)</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ccc6c580-6047-4244-8720-44f0f5e31caf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-91066761-2f33-4a5d-9ab7-424c822c2bc7\">위장과 연결된 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0229ceb3-ea5c-470e-b426-b96999ea99eb\"><b>위유혈(胃兪穴)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-248a79b5-999c-4094-9040-518af12f5290\"> 등</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-810bbbf3-3bb0-4eb1-b103-8c952fa6a97c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2fb2ad5f-963b-447e-a93b-2233503ad27a\">각 장기와 연관된 배수혈이 등 뒤에 줄줄이 배열되어 있어요.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cfaf65a6-5cc9-4663-9c2f-76b1b2396718\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-597abc2a-1f08-45a5-b1aa-f078d94069a3\">​</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cdb2aa93-3b5e-4d6c-97d8-370dfe2b7bfe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-609fbf54-0034-451b-88db-d86c6b7dcf81\">이러한 경혈을 자극하면 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-edad546a-f278-495d-8a45-379f56c25a5a\"><b>해당 장기의 기능을 도와주고, </b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f66f6d1b-a8a6-4d4e-9dd2-134b1c9a7e1c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7388a686-a7c3-4861-b88b-e0c96f3a75da\"><b>기혈 순환을 원활하게</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9cbd978a-16b9-496b-baf2-892961c7796e\"> 만들어줍니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4bf8e018-5f6d-46b3-939e-e459aa8664fe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9ba095bc-f298-4878-8474-b98437c68986\">쉽게 말해, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-79800cb1-e767-45c8-acae-b9bf992328a5\"><b>등을 관리하면 속이 편해지고, 몸 안 장기가 회복되는 효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d9f95df6-f4cc-4129-bb51-56840eec74c8\">를 </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-26ec4bb5-f36d-4526-9d2f-860e779ed44d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8137f9c0-7d3e-41a0-8ce4-b293253b468f\">기대할 수 있는 거죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7733008b-a637-4545-96f8-87f9e44e89cb\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-5f732b61-9eb0-4f4d-b85b-0e430a37be3d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a25f458b-b735-4391-96d5-569643b57f7e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7afa2c96-357e-4a14-b25e-0440ee51c471\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bfa5ab81-261f-4980-8a58-bf3369244cb1\"><b>왜 배수혈 관리가 중요한가요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7fb49d72-df94-46c6-a58c-46f99d1dc4f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-47947748-7e35-438b-b7f2-d23682f36564\">📌 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5ddf69e8-c5b5-48f3-ac89-f262006f4de2\"><b>현대인의 생활습관</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-24afee3d-2dfd-4212-8a77-50f22407c396\">은 배수혈 건강을 해치기 쉽습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-31aff15b-5c9a-4118-ad10-e60e9fb0e81b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-397001f6-7efc-4ad3-a4c2-212b71d0e495\">오랜 컴퓨터 사용, 스마트폰 사용, 스트레스, 나쁜 자세 등이 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7a9f010c-ae24-4748-a356-eb93854f9f5b\"><b>등 근육을 긴장시키고, 경혈 흐름을 막아 </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ec798459-3aae-4c3b-b1ba-e11a4bbc6f02\">기혈순환 장애로 이어지기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9e5a1054-fab0-4a1c-9b50-e36ac7c27a1b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8d6d1bf0-1715-4dad-99f0-acc2fcae592b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-27357366-dab9-4d2a-b4a4-a1473d016d68\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-32122810-09dd-4928-ae61-38ebd99911b5\">📌 특히, 자율신경이 예민한 분들일수록</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d11ed75-4717-4252-ab7e-d86de063aff6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4f6406f5-8743-4617-aebe-13796366643f\"><b>등이 뻐근하거나 눌리듯 아프고, 이유 없는 피로감</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-da6a70fd-e61e-4ae7-a1f1-32c83825d2f9\">을 호소하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fac1b31f-acc6-4b0d-b17f-60a7eb1b7edd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-40d39def-42e1-4bf6-bcdd-3eeec9ea335d\">이럴 때 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9b309b78-f182-4839-aefc-c2805e14d57c\"><b>배수혈을 중심으로 한 침, 뜸, 부항 치료</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6dae9946-597b-4202-93a3-26276f095364\">는 큰 도움이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-a25f458b-b735-4391-96d5-569643b57f7e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00edb31c-8a50-427b-a446-1d4584b5c11c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-00edb31c-8a50-427b-a446-1d4584b5c11c\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9c3d450cd714ca55.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://is