3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bdc90e5d-f1a2-491c-8824-956f0d94176a\">✔️ 장기 기능 강화 (예: 위장, 폐, 심장 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b5f7c1b-bb4d-4e8e-910a-bad362e574ab\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-26935b24-4fb5-4970-8eac-32c0bf12aea2\">✔️ 피로 회복과 기력 보강</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5a8b0573-57d8-4044-a6ae-9608a09a5ac0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-4030b1c5-8eef-492f-b0a2-aeebdb8ff7ef\">✔️ 스트레스 완화 및 자율신경 안정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ce685f52-657b-4990-bd15-be81749bd479\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d10520db-2191-40f1-bd52-9d024a987e5e\">✔️ 면역력 향상</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d1440bee-f667-43cd-99d6-dac9a163458a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-94252e2d-0dcf-415c-b5a0-f46bdf78da85\">✔️ 등·어깨 결림 해소</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-222f973d-db24-4e39-854a-7ed4475226b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-71fc1cdd-f17e-42ff-9ae6-0ff3b19ac4b9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bef64ac5-8fac-4b1f-aae7-d682060fd917\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-276e3be4-9cae-4d17-85d3-ca76b9b7b1ba\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ad123b9d-ebe9-4d18-8195-76308f69989c\"><b>에서는 </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1eb7ae5a-d676-4c93-8f33-0fefd6fee12a\">각 개인의 체질과 증상에 맞춰, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d368f49d-dafd-4d18-b30b-69968b1795e5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2af6d055-7ee7-405d-9dc5-886f258f3149\">필요한 배수혈을 선별해 안전하게 자극합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2892d2f1-2cf6-4d10-a20d-7494f99c29f4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-887d6601-0256-49e9-ab75-6a98c212b68f\">일시적인 통증 완화가 아니라, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-27bf3d71-7148-4ec8-b4e2-c4fe9c65ff8b\"><b>몸속 깊은 회복</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-51068590-0191-4c0d-a6eb-4abeceec2048\">을 이끌어내는 치료를 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3dc779e2-28d7-4627-9d1d-d958315b3e52\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-95e49641-b764-4bc2-aaf5-904ad8e17650\">지향합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-486b7cec-db48-4169-88da-fb44e7233bb5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\" >\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-d3848c85-15c9-4f0f-abcf-66f8fa7e18de\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"t